fields.name: Fender Deluxe Roadhouse Stratocaster, Classic Copper
fields.description: The Fender Deluxe Roadhouse Stratocaster Electric Guitar offers musicians a versatile tone with classic playability. The Alder body has a naturally bright tone with a warm body, making it ideal for achieving the notorious Stratocaster sound. The Maple fingerboard produces a wealth of complex overtones, whilst the 12'' radius provides a suitable surface for lead riffs and sweeping bends. The three Vintage Noiseless pickups have five accessible combinations that produce clear notes with no hum. This model also features a V6 rotary switch which determines how your pickups are pushed. This model features a highly durable classic copper gloss finish, so your guitar will look as good as it sounds.

fields.name: Gibson ES-335 Figured Electric Guitar, Antique Natural
fields.description:
Gleaming with quality. The Gibson ES-335 Figured guitar will simply take your breath away. Its stunning looks are just the start - it's dripping with warm, articulate, vintage tone. The Calibrated T-Type humbuckers provide you with all the articulation and clarity you could wish for, whilst offering the perfect tonal range. And the thermally engineered centreblock provides this semi-hollow guitar with unrivalled stability and sustain. You'll be riffing all day long on this tonal masterpiece.

Play for days. The playability of this sublime guitar is something to be marvelled at. With a rounded, C shaped mahogany neck, your hand will feel like it can glide along like a bird. The luscious rosewood fretboard is warm and smooth, providing you with heaps of sustain and a super smooth feel. It would be criminal not to mention the beautiful AAA flame maple top, which boasts a superb finish and beautiful resonance. It's almost too easy to fall in love with this guitar at first sight. But once you've heard it, there's simply no going back.

fields.name: Martin GPC-X2E Macassar Acoustic Guitar
fields.description:
Solid-topped tonal charm. It's indulgent. And it's all oozing from the Martin GPC-X2E Macassar. It delivers all that unmistakable Martin flair you crave with the ability to sound even better with age and the more you play. Crafted under the ethos of unparalleled tone, masterful design, and flawless playability, it's easy to see why Martin are leading the industry...

Still hand-made. A standard Martin proudly holds close to their hearts, bringing you exquisite craftsmanship infused with legendary quality. You won't be disappointed. Explore a gorgeous, melodic, responsive voice that's perfect for a multitude of genres and techniques while an all-purpose, easy-playing GPC body provides a flawless playing feel as well as unrestricted access to upper frets. You can also enjoy all its glorious tone, amplified. All thanks to responsive, quality Fishman electronics. The spotlight awaits...

fields.name: Taylor Big Baby Acoustic Guitar, Natural
fields.description: The Taylor Big Baby Acoustic Guitar is the bigger version of Taylor’s baby guitar, delivering the comfort and portability of the small body whilst boasting a larger size and incredibly full voice. It’s small dreadnought body is crafted from a sitka spruce top with sapele back and sides, producing a dynamic range of tone with excellent versatility. The guitar also features a nubone nut and saddle, die-cast tuners, a tortoise pickguard, and an ebony fingerboard. At 15/16th scale, the Big Baby Taylor Guitar will sit right at home with experienced players and new beginners alike.

fields.name: Fender 75th Anniversary Precision Bass Guitar
fields.description:
Long live the legend. After 75 years in the business, Fender knows a thing or two about building bass guitars. The Fender 75th Anniversary Precision Bass brings together those years of experience for a truly spectacular result. The unmistakable sound of a 50's P-bass pickup gives this anniversary model unbeatable low-mid punch, with a present and sparkling top end to boot, while its four-saddle bridge allows impeccable tuning consistency and intonation.

A real show-stopper. This 75th Anniversary P Bass sports an all-new, Diamond Anniversary metallic finish, with an eye-catching headstock to match. Its satin-finished, maple neck's 'Modern C' profile is exquisitely ergonomic, and will have you racing up and down the fingerboard with ease. It's ready for the road too, with a deluxe Fender gig bag included as standard. The original, iconic Fender P-Bass changed everything - and with a 75th Anniversary Precision in hand, you can make your mark too.

fields.name: Music Man Bongo 6 HH Bass Guitar, Stealth Black
fields.description: The Music Man Bongo 6 HH Bass is a unique electric bass guitar with some of the most powerful pickups ever. Loaded with dual Neodymium Humbucking Pickups, the Bongo 4 has an incredibly high output and offers bright sounds with plenty of precision. The 6 String Bongo features a 4 Band Active Preamp giving you access to more varied sounds and a rare active bass. Crafted in the USA to the highest standards, the Music Man Bongo 6 features an all basswood body providing excellent tone definition and a maple neck coupled with an ebony fingerboard for bright and clear sounds. With 6 strings, the Bongo 6 has an extended range which gives the opportunity of chording and playing melodies. This Bongo 6 HH Bass is finished in a sleek Stealth Black gloss finish.

fields.name: Dunlop Cotton Strap, Black
fields.description: The Dunlop cotton guitar strap brings comfort and durability together for a reliable way to secure your guitar. Using real leather ends, the strap is sure to not break under your guitar's weight. The cotton material is comfortable so you will be able to concentrate on your performance. The strap is a solid black colour for a smart look that will be appropriate to any guitar.

fields.name: Kinsman Hardshell Guitar Case, Brown
fields.description: The Kinsman Vintage Hard Shell case provides you with years of safe guitar transportation. Fitted with double brown leather grain textured cloth, retro style stitched valance and four gold coloured clip-over catches it looks the part too. The case also comes with a padded body surround compartment, lightweight wooden shell, neck support and a hinged lid storage compartment for all your guitar accessories. This case really is the perfect mix of style and security!

fields.name: Ernie Ball Regular Slinky Nickel Guitar Strings 10-46
fields.description: Give your guitar a new lease of life. The Ernie Ball Regular Slinky Nickel Strings promise clear, dynamic sound as well as brilliant robustness. Ernie Ball have set the standard for electric strings, they are iconic and have been used by the likes of Eric Clapton, Slash, and John Mayor. So, you know you can trust in them. Better still, they will arrive to you in Element Shield packaging which protects them against humidity, meaning they are fresh and ready to play.

fields.name: Planet Waves Classic Series 1/4" Instrument Cable, Right Angle, 20ft
fields.description: Superb quality with fantastic value. The Planet Waves Classic Series 1/4" Instrument Cable is a must-have accessory for live work. It features a handy 20ft length, making it perfect for those of wanting a little more room to showboat your talents across the stage. Or flaunt your persona and move around your rehearsal room. And, of course, it comes infused with world renowned Planet Waves quality for a pure, clean signal and a seamless, uninterrupted performance. Every time.

fields.name: Pearl Export EXX 22'' 6pc Drum Kit, High Voltage Blue
fields.description: Everything you need to start playing straight away! The Pearl Export EXX 22'' 6pc Drum Kit includes a full range drum kit, Sabian SBR cymbals and Pearl hardware, to give you an excellent introduction into drumming. Known around the world as one of the most popular kits on the market, the Pearl Export Series has been one of the top-selling drum kits for the last 30 years. Featuring 6-ply poplar and Asian mahogany for a crisp, warm tone which complements a range of drumming styles. The drums are each fitted with Remo drum heads, offering enhanced responses and sensitivity for maximum playability. The Pearl Export kit features durable chrome hardware which adds to the structural integrity of the shells, increasing durability, whilst complementing the stunning high-voltage blue finish.

fields.name: Mapex Tornado III 22'' Rock Drum Kit, Burgundy w/ Extra Crash
fields.description:
The best place to start playing the drums. There's a reason why the Mapex Tornado is considered the best entry-level drum kit around. The series offers unmatched quality for its accessible price. And there's no need to worry about buying any extras. This kit includes everything you need to get behind the skins and play: the 5-piece Mapex Tornado III drum kit as well as cymbals, hardware, stool and a pair of drumsticks. Play straight from the box.

Why should new learners have to settle for less? The Tornado drum shells are made from thick, hand-selected basswood, providing loud, resonant sounds and bright attack in any setting. This 22" Rock Fusion configuration is perfect for a variety of genres, so you'll have no trouble finding your favourite style. The included double-braced hardware offers both the durability and reliability you'll need for years of rehearsals and gigs. There's no instrument quite like the drums, and with the Mapex Tornado, you'll soon want to be a drummer for life.

This bundle includes an extra 16" crash cymbal with an accompanying cymbal boom stand!

fields.name: DW Drums Performance Series 14" x 6.5" Snare Drum, Ebony Stain
fields.description: The DW Drums Performance Series 14" x 6.5" snare in Ebony Stain brings you renowned DW quality and innovative maple HVX shells. This drum really sings and kicks out a loud, open tone that's perfect for the stage but can easily be reigned in for studio work. This responsive snare captures all the subtle nuances of any playing style and allows individual drummers to shine. Plus, with double threaded centre lugs and a hand-sprayed specialty lacquer finish, this drum looks as good as it sounds.

fields.name: Pearl EXX Export 12" Rack Tom, Black
fields.description: Great value, Pearl quality. The Pearl EXX Export 12" Rack Tom is ideal for adding to your EXX Export kit, or using creatively as part of a custom setup. With a blended mahogany and poplar shell, you get a tone that is bright, warm and punchy. The low mass lugs and SST (Superior Shell Technology) further sets EXX apart from other affordable drums on the market.

fields.name: Pearl EXX 18" x 16" Floor Tom, Jet Black
fields.description: Build your own Export kit. Or pick up a formidable auxiliary floor tom. The Pearl EXX 18" x 16" Floor Tom offers thumping low-end with superb resonance. Quality and value wrapped up in a single package, it's the quintessential floor tom for beginner and intermediate players. More advanced, working drummers will also make use of it in any musical application. With Pearl's Superior Shell Technology (SST), the end result is a floor tom that's as hard as iron but resonant and tonally adept on every level. Meanwhile, the Low Mass Lugs provide minimal shell interaction - maximising sustain when you need it most. You'll have more full-bodied low-end and rich resonance than ever before. The EXX Export Floor Tom will make an outstanding addition to your shell set-up.

fields.name: Vic Firth American Classic 5B Hickory Drumsticks
fields.description:
When you think of 5B drumsticks, there's one pair that comes to mind. The Vic Firth American Classic 5B Hickory Drumsticks. Whilst being slightly thicker and heavier than a standard 5A stick, the classics 5B's are suitable to cover all styles. They provide a bit more punch for your funk and rock grooves. And, made by Vic Firth - you know you're getting your money's worth.


But why would you choose the Vic Firth 5B? They are made from a special hickory that is ideal for drumsticks. They are durable, reliable. You can use them for months because they undergo a rigorous manufacturing process that goes above and beyond expectations. The ones that don't make it are used to heat the kiln. The Vic Firth sticks aren't just another 5B, they are their own instrument. An instrument that has been the drummer's go-to choice for decades.

fields.name: Shure PGADRUMKIT4 Drum Microphone Kit, 4 Piece
fields.description:
Pro sound for your kit. The Shure PGADRUMKIT4 Drum Microphone Kit gives you everything you need to capture the power of percussion. From the crack of a snare, to the deep thump of a kick.

Kickstart your mic collection. Each microphone has a unique character, tailored to compliment different types of drum. Whether you're on stage or in the studio, you'll get accurate sound, every single time.

Rigorously tested, Shure have built these mics to withstand serious wear and tear. Thanks to a tough, metallic construction, even accidental drum hits won't break them. The PGA Drum Kit 4 is essential if you need solid sound with long-lasting reliability.

fields.name: Yamaha HS8 MP Studio Monitors, Matched Pair
fields.description:
Factory matched parts deliver superior audio performance. The Yamaha HS8 MP, Matched Pair are special-edition versions of the award-winning studio monitors. The premium-grade nearfield design combines parts matched by their serial number to deliver the best possible acoustic performance.


The HS8 Studio Monitor provides an extended frequency response for optimal audio fidelity, capturing every nuance from your source audio. The high-definition audio is ideal for mixing and mastering applications, recreating your sound in extreme detail. The flat response stays true to the original sound, allowing you to achieve the best possible mix.
The Yamaha HS8 also includes attenuators for Room Control and High Trim for added flexibility, allowing you to improve the performance of your monitor based on your room.

fields.name: Adam Audio T5V Studio Monitors, Pair
fields.description: The Adam Audio T5V Studio Monitors (Pair) are a pair of professional 2-way nearfield monitors offering extremely high performance, high dynamic range, a wide frequency range and an extremely wide sweet spot, making them ideal for music production, post-production and more. The T5V monitors provide up to 106dB, with a 5-inch 50W woofer providing deep and tight lows, and a new 1.9-inch U-ART tweeter delivering precise and controlled highs. The T5V monitors offer fine tune control, allowing you to boost and cut the high/low frequencies for optimum performance depending on their position in a room. The fine tuning controls, combined with high performance and a wide sweet spot, deliver a highly accurate sound, allowing you to create crisp, punchy, full mixes and productions.

fields.name: Focusrite Scarlett Solo (3rd Gen)
fields.description:
The best-sounding Scarlett mic preamp yet. The Focusrite Scarlett Solo (3rd Gen) is the third generation of the popular Scarlett series, featuring a 2-in/2-out configuration and Air-enabled mic preamps.

The Scarlett Solo (3rd Gen) Audio Interface is one of the most affordable yet great-sounding interfaces on the market. The interface includes class-leading 24-bit/192kHz AD-DA converters, delivering pristine sound quality. It features everything you need to record vocals and instruments, including built-in Phantom Power for use with condenser microphones.

The low-latency, rock-solid USB driver allows you to monitor and record in near real-time. It also comes complete with a comprehensive music software suite including Ableton Live 10 Lite, Focusrite's Red Plug-In Suite and three months of free access to Splice Sounds. It's the perfect interface for beginners and professionals alike, providing you with everything you need to get achieve studio-grade recordings.

fields.name: SSL 2 2-Channel USB Audio Interface
fields.description:
High-end SSL technology for your personal studio. The SSL 2 2-Channel USB Audio Interface is a compact interface, allowing you to bring the legendary SSL sound, wherever you go.

Solid State Logic has long been a powerhouse in the music world for their sought-after gear, with some of the world's most famous artists and producers using SSL. This interface provides you with two SSL-designed analog microphone preamps, providing 24-bit/192kHz for the best possible audio fidelity. The result is pristine sound and crystal-clear playback, with a front-panel low-latency monitor mix control.

Add extra analog character by using the "Legacy 4K mode", inspired by vintage SSL consoles. It provides added sparkle, perfect for use with vocal recordings. In addition to this, the interface comes complete with the SSL Production Pack, including SSL Native plugins, DAWs, samples, loops and virtual instruments. Experience why SSL is such a legend in the world of audio gear and pick up the SSL 2 today.

fields.name: Steinberg Cubase Pro 11
fields.description:
Steinberg Cubase Pro 11 is here to bring you the latest and greatest tools, effects and virtual instruments that will refresh your approach to production and performance.

From Deadmau5 to the Weeknd. Thanks to its high-quality sounds and intuitive interface, Cubase has long been one of the most in-demand DAWs on the market and is used by many professionals. Cubase Pro 11 builds on the legacy of 10.5, providing you with all new SpectraLayers, 90 high-end audio and MIDI VST effect processors, eight powerful instruments with over 3,400 sounds, as well as a 64-bit floating-point engine.

Cubase Pro 11 is the perfect accompaniment to any musical journey. Whether you're a budding beginner, or a seasoned pro with numerous Grammys on their shelf, this DAW will allow you to realise your true creative vision, without any compromises. Just as comfortable taking on Blockbuster scores as it is songwriter demos, no task will feel out of reach. There's no awkward navigation, or endless seas of menus, its refined layout allows you to focus on what's most important. It's all about the music.

fields.name: Native Instruments Komplete 13
fields.description:
Everyone's favourite virtual instrument bundle just got better! Meet the latest addition to Native Instrument's library - Komplete 13. Your approach to production and performance will be rejuvenated thanks to its vast content. It comes complete with 65 high-quality instruments and effects, as well as 35,000 sounds, and 20+ expansions. Thanks to the seemingly infinite number of options, you'll be covered for any genre, or musical style thrown at you.

Don't waste time reading manuals. Jump right in and get creative. Komplete 13 is incredibly easy to install. Simply plug-in the HDD, open Native access and you're good to go. What's more, upon registering your product you'll receive a 22GBP E-voucher to spend in the NI online store. This is the ideal collection for any serious musician, and producer looking to expand their sound.
